videos.headline: UCF RB's 64-yard gain sets up 1st-and-goal
videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Adrian Killins Jr., who burst for 64 yards to set up first-and-goal for UCF.

videos.headline: UCF Milton runs in 5-yard TD
videos.description: On a quarterback draw, McKenzie Milton extends the ball and scores 5-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Milton rips 24-yard TD pass
videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton connects with a wide-open Gabriel Davis for 24-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Pitt's Araujo-Lopes returns punt for 86-yard TD
videos.description: Pitt's Rafael Araujo-Lopes fields the punt and eludes UCF tacklers for a 86-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UCF's interception stalls Pitt's drive
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett's pass is intercepted by UCF's Richie Grant, who returns it 25 yards.

videos.headline: Colubiale grabs and scores TD
videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton throws to Michael Colubiale, who gets a foot down to score a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UCF's Milton connects with Anderson for 13-yard TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds his fourth different receiver for a touchdown as he throws to Otis Anderson for a 13-yard score.

videos.headline: Pitt's Ffrench runs in a 58-yard TD
videos.description: On a pitch pass by QB Kenny Pickett, Pitt RB Maurice Ffrench eludes UCF defenders for a 58-yard touchdown.
